&lt;!doctype html&gt;
&lt;html lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
  &lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&rdquo; /&gt;
  &lt;title&gt;Privacy Policy&lt;/title&gt;
  &lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&rdquo; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1&rdquo; /&gt;
  &lt;meta name=&quot;robots&rdquo; content=&quot;noindex,follow&rdquo; /&gt;
  &lt;style&gt;
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
    body { margin: 0; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; }
    header, main, footer { max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.25rem; }
    h1, h2, h3 { line-height: 1.25; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.9rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.35rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; }
    p, li { font-size: 1rem; }
    ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    code { background: rgba(127,127,127,.15); padding: .1rem .25rem; border-radius: 4px; }
    .meta { color: #666; font-size: .95rem; }
    .notice { background: rgba(255, 230, 0, 0.12); border-left: 4px solid #e0c200; padding: .75rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
    a { color: #0b6; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    footer { color: #666; font-size: .95rem; }
  &lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
  &lt;header&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Privacy Policy&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;Effective date: &lt;time datetime=&quot;2025-10-08&quot;&gt;October 8, 2025&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p class=&quot;meta&quot;&gt;Controller: Eager Plumbing LLC, 418 Clay St, Kerrville, TX 78028, US · Email: privacy@eagerplumbingtx.com&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;notice&quot;&gt;
      This policy explains what data is collected, how it is used and shared, and the rights available under applicable laws such as GDPR and CCPA/CPRA. 
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/header&gt;

  &lt;main&gt;
    &lt;section id=&quot;scope&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Scope&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;This policy applies to the website and mobile applications operated by Eager Plumbing LLC and related services provided globally.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;data-we-collect&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Data We Collect&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Account data: name, email, username, password (hashed).&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Usage data: IP address, device and browser, pages viewed, timestamps.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Transaction data: orders, billing details, limited payment metadata via processor.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Marketing preferences: subscriptions and communication settings.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Cookies/trackers: identifiers for analytics, functionality, and ads where applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Data is collected directly, automatically through the service, and from service providers as described below.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;purposes-legal-bases&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Purposes and Legal Bases&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Provide and maintain services (Contract).&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Security, fraud prevention, and debugging (Legitimate interests).&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Compliance with legal obligations (Legal obligation).&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Analytics and improvement (Legitimate interests or Consent, depending on jurisdiction).&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Marketing communications (Consent, with opt-out options).&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;how-we-process&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;How We Process&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Data is processed via forms, account features, automatic logs, cookies, and third-party processors (e.g., payments, analytics, hosting, email delivery).&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;No automated decision-making or profiling with legal effects is performed unless stated otherwise.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;sharing&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Sharing and Disclosures&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Payment processors to process transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Analytics providers to measure and improve performance.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Cloud hosting and storage vendors to deliver the service.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Email service providers for transactional and marketing emails.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Disclosures may occur for legal compliance, to protect rights and safety, or during business transfers.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;rights&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Your Rights&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Depending on location, rights may include access, rectification, erasure, restriction, portability, objection, and the right to withdraw consent.&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;To exercise rights, send a request to privacy@eagerplumbingtx.com. Reasonable identity verification may be required. Responses are provided within the timeframes set by law.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;retention&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Data Retention&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Account data is retained for the life of the account and a reasonable period thereafter.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Transaction records are retained for statutory periods (for example, up to 7 years).&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Usage and cookie data is retained per cookie lifetimes or aggregated/anonymized.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;security&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Security&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Measures include TLS encryption in transit, access controls, monitoring and logging, and vendor due diligence including DPAs where required.&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;No method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and residual risk cannot be eliminated.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;cookies&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Cookies and Tracking&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Types include strictly necessary, functional, analytics, and advertising cookies. Non-essential cookies may require consent depending on jurisdiction.&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Preferences can be managed via the cookie banner or browser settings, and can be changed at any time.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;transfers&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;International Transfers&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Where data is transferred internationally, appropriate safeguards such as Standard Contractual Clauses or adequacy decisions are used.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;children&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Children’s Privacy&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;The service is not directed to children below applicable age thresholds, and data is not knowingly collected from them.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;changes&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Changes to This Policy&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Material changes will be posted with an updated effective date, and additional notice may be provided where required.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;contact&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Contact&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;p&gt;Questions or requests: privacy@eagerplumbingtx.com. Individuals may have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority in their jurisdiction.&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;

    &lt;hr /&gt;

    &lt;section id=&quot;jurisdictional-notices&quot;&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Jurisdictional Notices&lt;/h2&gt;

      &lt;h3&gt;GDPR (EEA/UK)&lt;/h3&gt;
      &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Lawful bases are listed above; data subjects have the rights listed in the Rights section.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Transfers outside the EEA/UK rely on appropriate safeguards such as SCCs or adequacy decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;

      &lt;h3&gt;California (CCPA/CPRA)&lt;/h3&gt;
      &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;California residents have rights to know, delete, correct, and opt out of sale or sharing of personal information.&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Two or more methods will be provided to submit requests; an opt-out mechanism is available for targeted advertising where applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;
  &lt;/main&gt;

  &lt;footer&gt;
    90 2025 Eager Plumbing LLC
  &lt;/footer&gt;

  &lt;script&gt;
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  &lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
